Summary: this has been here since sept 30, 2011
divs: Sighting Details Went out side to see if the ufo was still here and it is. It was very bright in the sky and had objects shooting out of it. There appered to be a ufo off to the northeast. I knew it was our friend they have been here since the 30th of sept 2011. They were obscured by clouds for a few days but are now visable. It stayed in the sky hovering and ejecting objects out of it. The light pulsated as did the one to the northeast. I lost sight of the object because I went inside, it is getting colder at night here.
